\n<Udo>\FF[\V[4]]Minato, did you find it? There's no need to run
away, right?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Well, it's not like that... I just came to
take a bath...

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Oh, what a coincidence♪ Shall we take a
bath together then?

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF](You're such a blatant liar... I was thinking
of holding back until tomorrow, but I've
changed my mind.)

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]How about this view? It's quite something,
isn't it?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]I know... I just entered a little while
ago...

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Eh... but today is supposed to be free
time...
